    "long_instructions": "# Do This\r\n1. Create three functions called `collect_paint`, `navigate_to_new_location`, and `paint_a_path`.\r\n#\r\n2. `collect_paint` should use a `while painter.is_on_bucket` loop.\r\n#\r\n3. `navigate_to_new_location` should use a `while painter.can_move` loop.\r\n#\r\n4. `paint_a_path` should use the `paint()` and `move()` methods.\r\n#\r\n5. Use all three functions together to navigate and paint throughout the Neighborhood.\r\n    - Hint: Remember to use the `turn_left()` and `turn_right()` functions as needed.\r\n    \r\n6. Run your code and observe how the Painter collects paint, navigates to a new spot, and paints a path.\r\n",
